'''Andrew Foley''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed the [[Hepsalum Tash]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the sixteen years and older category. He was twenty-five at the time his entry was published.

